Plugins,
In Dashboard->Manage Jenkins->Plugins->select available tab & in search type ->Git


Click on New Item,
Give name & select Freestyle project -> Save.

Dashboard->GitJenkinsIntegration->Configuration,
  Popup will be opened. On that Pop up,
   SourceCode Management -> Enable Git radio button.
   Give url which is from the github->Code->url(Repository url)
   In Build Triggers->Enable "Poll SCM".
   Inside schedule, *  *  *  *  * (Mins,Hours,Days,Month,Year)
   In Build Step->py GitJenkins.py
   Apply & Save.
   
Then Run it.
